title: THE NZ DIGITAL WORKPLACE CONFERENCE
eventShortDescription:
​The 8th Annual New Zealand DIGITAL WORKPLACE CONFERENCE
(previously the SharePoint Conference) by ShareThePoint Ltd is now “The Digital Workplace Conference” – same quality, more content, and a wider audience.

This is a unique opportunity to participate in two days of unequalled learning, with around 400 delegates, international speakers and a unique opportunity to connect, communicate and collaborate while learning everything about the Digital Workplace! 
Don't miss out on experiencing our 21st event! *

(*across Australia, New Zealand and SouthEast Asia).
